triggered_conditions: The 'emergencyWithdrawToken' function allows the owner to withdraw any token from the contract, including user-deposited tokens.
The 'emergencyWithdrawBNB' function allows the owner to withdraw all BNB from the contract.
attack_path_summary: The function call sequence allows the contract owner to withdraw all user-deposited tokens and BNB from the contract, effectively draining the contract of its assets.
